                "followup-update"
              ]
            },
            "description": "⚠️ AUTHENTICATION REQUIRED\n\nUpdate followup status for an order\n\nRequired:\n- id: Order ID\n- followup_call: 0 or 1\n\nOptional:\n- followup_note: Note text\n- followup_label: Label key (interested, highly_interested, need_time, etc.)\n\nResponse includes:\n- emp_id: Employee ID who updated\n- follow_by: Employee name who updated"
